# AXIOM validator seed list — 6-column format
#
#   "name", "validator_id (64 hex = blake3(sphincs_pk))", "ed25519_pk (64 hex, or empty)",
#   "proof_cap (dmap|zkvm)", "fee_rate (e.g. 1%, 0.08%, 0)", "carriers"
#
# validator_id is the cryptographic identity used for S-ABR overlap comparison.
# name is a free-form operator label — UI/logs only, safely renameable.
# fee_rate honored as offered_fee = max(MIN_FEE, amount * rate_bps / 10_000) per witness.
#
